                    <h2 class="image-text-banner__title">Joining the Army</h2>
            
                    <div class="image-text-banner__description rte">
                        <p>To join the Army, you need to meet a set of basic requirements. These include telling us about your age, nationality, health and fitness. We will also ask you about your education and qualifications, but this is to help to find the right role for you. You can still join the Army if you have no formal qualifications.</p>
                    </div>


                    <a class="image-text-banner__cta-btn cta-btn cta-btn--primary" data-target-content-id="2303" href="/army-careers/careers/entry-requirements-and-standards/"><span class="cta-btn__bg"></span><span class="cta-btn__text">
                        Can I join?
