            <div class="image-text-banner__content-col">
                    <ul class="image-text-banner__tagline">
                        <li>Army Life</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="image-text-banner__title">The Army is its people</h2>
            
                    <div class="image-text-banner__description rte">
                        <p>What makes the British Army? Its not the weaponry or the vehicles  its the people.</p>
<p>Our vision is a competitive, adaptable and inclusive Army imbued with an unwavering will to win; where people feel they belong; where their talent is nurtured, where health is positively promoted, and opportunity maximised.</p>
                    </div>

                    
